  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK746">
<l>ellāp poruḷu muṭaittā yiṭattutavu</l>
<l>nallā ḷuṭaiya taraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is that which has all (needful) things, and excellent heroes that can help it against destruction (by foes).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
